# Optional keys. The app runs fully FREE with neither set.
#
# Free street-level imagery (Mapillary). Create an app at
# https://www.mapillary.com/dashboard/developers to get a client token.
# Without it, the map still works; the street-level button is disabled.
VITE_MAPILLARY_TOKEN=

# Google Maps Platform key (billing enabled). When set, unlocks:
#   - Photorealistic 3D Tiles (true photoreal "from above")
#   - Google Street View panoramas
# WARNING: Photorealistic 3D Tiles free tier is tiny (~1,000 req/mo).
VITE_GOOGLE_MAPS_KEY=
